1
00:00:11,420 --> 00:00:12,420
Thank you

2
00:00:32,500 --> 00:00:34,460
Is going out for a late-night snack with me

3
00:00:34,460 --> 00:00:36,330
embarrassing you or something?

4
00:00:36,330 --> 00:00:38,500
Dressed like that—are you afraid of

5
00:00:38,500 --> 00:00:39,790
being recognized, or kidnapped?

6
00:00:40,960 --> 00:00:43,500
Rourou, you’ve got it all wrong

7
00:00:43,500 --> 00:00:46,380
I’ve got all kinds of connections out there

8
00:00:46,380 --> 00:00:48,710
and quite a few enemies too.

9
00:00:48,710 --> 00:00:49,920
I’m worried someone might show up while we're eating

10
00:00:49,920 --> 00:00:52,830
and smack me with a pig's head.

11
00:00:54,540 --> 00:00:56,670
Relax, no one here knows you

12
00:00:56,670 --> 00:00:58,540
except me

13
00:00:58,540 --> 00:01:00,750
Sir, do you know him?

14
00:01:01,750 --> 00:01:04,000
Keep it down

15
00:01:05,960 --> 00:01:07,290
What was that about?

16
00:01:07,290 --> 00:01:08,210
I told you—

17
00:01:08,210 --> 00:01:10,789
no one here’s gonna recognize you.

18
00:01:15,580 --> 00:01:16,750
Hurry up and eat

19
00:01:16,750 --> 00:01:18,670
or I’m finishing it all.

20
00:01:22,500 --> 00:01:23,670
Here

21
00:01:24,789 --> 00:01:26,670
I remember you’ve always had a sensitive tongue.

22
00:01:26,670 --> 00:01:29,580
That’s way too hot—how are you eating it?

23
00:01:29,580 --> 00:01:31,000
Let me cool it down for you.

24
00:01:36,789 --> 00:01:38,000
Pan Hao

25
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:42,670
Don’t be so nice to me.

26
00:01:46,330 --> 00:01:48,789
If I’m not nice to you,

27
00:01:48,789 --> 00:01:50,750
should I be nice to that old guy behind you?

28
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:02,290
Okay, perfect temperature now

29
00:02:02,290 --> 00:02:03,290
Eat

30
00:02:11,250 --> 00:02:15,040
There’s somewhere I’ve always wanted to go.

31
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:17,750
Let’s go after this.

32
00:02:19,040 --> 00:02:21,790
Sure. Wherever you wanna go,

33
00:02:21,790 --> 00:02:23,170
I'm in.

34
00:02:27,540 --> 00:02:29,500
Here—your favorite.

35
00:02:29,500 --> 00:02:30,540
Thanks

36
00:02:50,880 --> 00:02:52,000
It’s so beautiful.

37
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:04,920
I’ve imagined this moment a thousand times.

38
00:03:06,920 --> 00:03:09,210
Standing here

39
00:03:09,210 --> 00:03:12,000
looking out at the skyline…

40
00:03:13,540 --> 00:03:15,920
with you by my side.

41
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:21,579
This exact scene

42
00:03:21,579 --> 00:03:23,420
has appeared in my mind countless times

43
00:03:34,790 --> 00:03:35,920
Pan Hao

44
00:03:37,710 --> 00:03:39,500
We...

45
00:03:40,420 --> 00:03:41,920
Let's be together...

46
00:03:53,540 --> 00:03:54,670
Are you serious?

47
00:03:59,130 --> 00:04:04,290
Even after all these years apart…

48
00:04:04,290 --> 00:04:07,170
I don't know if you're any different

49
00:04:07,170 --> 00:04:09,040
than who you were

50
00:04:10,040 --> 00:04:13,170
I still want to give it a shot.

51
00:04:19,540 --> 00:04:21,880
Just so you know—

52
00:04:21,880 --> 00:04:25,420
No refunds, no returns

53
00:04:25,420 --> 00:04:27,380
and no trial period either.

54
00:05:09,580 --> 00:05:11,540
Thanks for the ride,

55
00:05:11,540 --> 00:05:13,790
my dear Mr. Pan

56
00:05:14,750 --> 00:05:17,210
Just got yourself a handsome boyfriend…

57
00:05:17,210 --> 00:05:20,210
already getting used to having the chauffeured service?

58
00:05:20,210 --> 00:05:21,670
or else?

59
00:05:21,670 --> 00:05:24,000
You're already mine

60
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,920
Isn’t this the least I should get?

61
00:05:27,170 --> 00:05:28,880
Whatever you said

62
00:05:29,830 --> 00:05:32,290
Off to work

63
00:05:33,080 --> 00:05:34,380
I'm leaving

64
00:05:36,540 --> 00:05:38,380
Hey, don't get too close to your clients

65
00:05:38,380 --> 00:05:40,170
at work

66
00:05:43,210 --> 00:05:44,630
Of course

67
00:05:44,630 --> 00:05:46,630
See whose name’s written on me?

68
00:05:46,630 --> 00:05:48,880
Sun Rourou

69
00:05:51,210 --> 00:05:53,920
I've really gotta go

70
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:58,290
Bye

71
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:03,170
Bye

72
00:06:18,170 --> 00:06:19,290
Time to catch up on sleep.

73
00:07:03,750 --> 00:07:05,670
Guys

74
00:07:05,670 --> 00:07:07,330
I’m up early for once—

75
00:07:07,330 --> 00:07:08,630
wait...

76
00:07:08,630 --> 00:07:10,790
Actually… I just haven’t slept yet.

77
00:07:10,790 --> 00:07:13,580
Brought you all a protein-packed feast.

78
00:07:13,580 --> 00:07:14,330
YuChuan

79
00:07:14,330 --> 00:07:15,170
help me to get the table set up

80
00:07:15,170 --> 00:07:17,080
Hurry, get moving!

81
00:07:17,080 --> 00:07:19,080
Look who finally showed up.

82
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:21,580
Who drained you dry last night?

83
00:07:21,580 --> 00:07:23,580
couldn't find you at all

84
00:07:23,580 --> 00:07:25,920
I’m still full of energy, alright?

85
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:27,540
Come on, everyone

86
00:07:27,540 --> 00:07:30,580
Thanks to you—

87
00:07:30,580 --> 00:07:33,330
I’m officially with Rourou.

88
00:07:33,330 --> 00:07:35,290
Nice

89
00:07:36,130 --> 00:07:37,170
Where's Chenghan?

90
00:07:38,250 --> 00:07:39,920
Seems like he took time off

91
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:43,130
to be with his sister for surgery.

92
00:07:43,130 --> 00:07:44,540
He has a sister?

93
00:07:44,960 --> 00:07:47,540
Weren’t you his middle school classmate?

94
00:07:47,540 --> 00:07:48,670
How do you not know that?

95
00:07:52,130 --> 00:07:53,790
Alright, guys

96
00:07:53,790 --> 00:07:55,500
You’ve all eaten the food, right?

97
00:07:55,500 --> 00:07:56,880
then you owe me one

98
00:07:56,880 --> 00:07:57,750
When I go take a nap later,

99
00:07:57,750 --> 00:07:59,290
no one’s allowed to wake me up.

100
00:07:59,290 --> 00:08:01,290
Good night

101
00:08:01,290 --> 00:08:03,000
I knew it—

102
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:04,630
nothing comes for free with you.

103
00:08:04,630 --> 00:08:07,420
Even if he didn’t treat us, we wouldn’t have bothered with him.

104
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:10,880
Give me one more chance.

105
00:08:10,880 --> 00:08:12,880
Asking for more chances?

106
00:08:12,880 --> 00:08:14,210
I was this close to breaking even.

107
00:08:14,210 --> 00:08:15,790
Please, please, please

108
00:08:16,210 --> 00:08:17,330
I can still borrow some more

109
00:08:17,330 --> 00:08:18,830
I can still borrow some more, please

110
00:08:18,830 --> 00:08:21,880
Borrow again? With what?

111
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:23,790
Broke and still gambling?

112
00:08:23,790 --> 00:08:25,290
Stop messing around here, get out

113
00:08:25,290 --> 00:08:26,130
Please, please, please

114
00:08:26,130 --> 00:08:27,000
Let me in again

115
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:27,880
Please, I can win

116
00:08:27,880 --> 00:08:28,580
I will win

117
00:08:28,580 --> 00:08:29,420
Get out

118
00:08:29,420 --> 00:08:30,210
Please, please, please

119
00:08:30,210 --> 00:08:31,080
Let me go in again

120
00:08:31,080 --> 00:08:31,750
I can make it happen

121
00:08:31,750 --> 00:08:32,750
I swear

122
00:08:32,750 --> 00:08:35,419
Hey, what are you guys doing?

123
00:08:40,289 --> 00:08:41,000
Biao

124
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,880
Brother Biao....

125
00:08:42,880 --> 00:08:46,210
I heard you've been going to casino lately?

126
00:08:46,210 --> 00:08:48,250
Where are the diamonds?

127
00:08:48,250 --> 00:08:49,830
You see...

128
00:08:49,830 --> 00:08:52,380
Look, hear me out

129
00:08:52,380 --> 00:08:54,960
I could’ve gotten it—

130
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:57,380
But I… just had bad luck

131
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:01,420
Listen

132
00:09:01,420 --> 00:09:02,290
Just give me more time.

133
00:09:02,290 --> 00:09:03,460
I can nail it

134
00:09:03,460 --> 00:09:05,790
Seriously

135
00:09:08,040 --> 00:09:10,130
Give you some more time?

136
00:09:12,420 --> 00:09:13,540
and who’s giving me time?

137
00:09:14,580 --> 00:09:16,290
Hey

138
00:09:22,460 --> 00:09:23,420
Three days

139
00:09:25,170 --> 00:09:27,130
I'll give you three days

140
00:09:27,130 --> 00:09:28,250
Okay

141
00:09:28,250 --> 00:09:31,750
Three days later,

142
00:09:31,750 --> 00:09:33,170
If I don’t see the diamonds—

143
00:09:39,130 --> 00:09:40,920
You’ll be collecting your own corpse.

144
00:09:41,540 --> 00:09:44,290
Okay, three days

145
00:09:45,830 --> 00:09:47,040
Don't let me down

146
00:10:16,540 --> 00:10:17,750
Let's drink together

147
00:10:27,750 --> 00:10:29,460
Come on over

148
00:10:29,460 --> 00:10:31,790
I’m in a great mood today.

149
00:10:31,790 --> 00:10:34,670
Bring me your smoothest talker—

150
00:10:34,670 --> 00:10:37,380
the hottest one to come and drink with me.

151
00:10:43,290 --> 00:10:45,500
Hi, sorry to keep you waiting.

152
00:10:47,380 --> 00:10:51,250
This is our top host at ACE—

153
00:10:51,250 --> 00:10:51,880
Hunter

154
00:10:51,880 --> 00:10:54,670
Come

155
00:10:54,670 --> 00:10:58,290
Beautiful, what should I call you?

156
00:10:58,290 --> 00:11:00,630
Just call me Yunru.

157
00:11:02,040 --> 00:11:04,420
So you’re the smoothest talker?

158
00:11:04,420 --> 00:11:05,630
That's right

159
00:11:05,630 --> 00:11:06,670
Good

160
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:13,880
Strong drinker

161
00:11:13,880 --> 00:11:16,920
Come

162
00:11:20,380 --> 00:11:22,040
Slow down

163
00:11:22,040 --> 00:11:23,540
no one’s competing with you.

164
00:11:25,420 --> 00:11:27,290
Easy for you to say

165
00:11:27,290 --> 00:11:29,540
If I drink slower—

166
00:11:29,540 --> 00:11:31,540
or order less—

167
00:11:31,540 --> 00:11:32,710
you’ll just

168
00:11:32,710 --> 00:11:35,750
run off to some richer lady, right?

169
00:11:35,750 --> 00:11:37,420
Why would I?

170
00:11:40,500 --> 00:11:45,380
You hosts are all the same—just sweet talk.

171
00:11:45,880 --> 00:11:48,080
Saying you love me—

172
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:51,080
saying I’m the only one—

173
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:52,290
and what happened?

174
00:11:56,250 --> 00:11:59,500
I’m eight millions in debt

175
00:11:59,500 --> 00:12:01,790
and being forced to drink and entertain men.

176
00:12:10,670 --> 00:12:12,000
Lin Yunru

177
00:12:13,630 --> 00:12:17,420
You used to be one of Leo’s regulars?

178
00:12:21,040 --> 00:12:23,420
Right

179
00:12:23,420 --> 00:12:25,790
I used to be a VIP here.

180
00:12:26,500 --> 00:12:28,460
Now?

181
00:12:28,460 --> 00:12:30,670
I'm broke

182
00:12:30,670 --> 00:12:32,420
and drowning in debt.

183
00:12:34,040 --> 00:12:38,420
Leo said he’d help me find a way to make money

184
00:12:38,420 --> 00:12:41,290
That “way” was

185
00:12:41,290 --> 00:12:44,290
to send me to a hostess club to drink with clients.

186
00:12:45,330 --> 00:12:50,420
Otherwise, I’d get my limbs broken.

187
00:12:57,330 --> 00:12:59,710
This is all your fault.

188
00:12:59,710 --> 00:13:00,750
All because of you lowlife bastards

189
00:13:00,750 --> 00:13:03,540
who scam women for money

190
00:13:10,130 --> 00:13:11,080
Calm down

191
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:13,040
Calm down first

192
00:13:13,040 --> 00:13:14,290
Calm down now

193
00:13:17,540 --> 00:13:21,000
I had enough

194
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:25,920
I don’t want to do this anymore.

195
00:13:31,420 --> 00:13:33,080
Chill out now

196
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:34,210
Tell me everything—

197
00:13:34,210 --> 00:13:36,380
what happened?

198
00:13:40,460 --> 00:13:42,630
At first,

199
00:13:42,630 --> 00:13:45,290
I just wanted someone to treat me well.

200
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:50,330
Someone who could comfort me

201
00:13:50,330 --> 00:13:53,540
and made me feel loved.

202
00:13:54,920 --> 00:13:57,630
I thought I could buy

203
00:13:57,630 --> 00:13:59,170
real love.

204
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:02,420
Turns out—

205
00:14:04,330 --> 00:14:06,330
the more

206
00:14:06,330 --> 00:14:10,250
I paid,

207
00:14:11,710 --> 00:14:13,250
the less I was loved.

208
00:14:16,580 --> 00:14:20,540
Leo said I could front it on credit

209
00:14:20,540 --> 00:14:22,250
since my credit is solid

210
00:14:22,250 --> 00:14:25,500
not like I wouldn't be able to pay it back

211
00:14:25,500 --> 00:14:27,460
Leo

212
00:14:27,460 --> 00:14:29,040
asked you to cover it upfront?

213
00:14:33,710 --> 00:14:36,210
At first, just a few hundred thousand.

214
00:14:36,210 --> 00:14:37,540
I figure it's okay

215
00:14:37,540 --> 00:14:39,170
as long as I can pay it back

216
00:14:40,250 --> 00:14:45,790
Then it snowballed to eight millions

217
00:14:45,790 --> 00:14:47,130
from one million

218
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:51,290
Eight millions?!

219
00:15:10,130 --> 00:15:11,290
Zhen

220
00:15:11,290 --> 00:15:13,330
Leo really went too far,

221
00:15:13,330 --> 00:15:15,040
scamming girls out of money is one thing,

222
00:15:15,040 --> 00:15:16,250
but that's not all

223
00:15:16,250 --> 00:15:16,960
The point is

224
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:17,880
he actually sent them to

225
00:15:17,880 --> 00:15:19,830
the hostess bars

226
00:15:19,830 --> 00:15:21,920
People like that should be chopped up

227
00:15:23,540 --> 00:15:24,250
I didn't know

228
00:15:24,250 --> 00:15:27,290
you were so righteous.

229
00:15:27,290 --> 00:15:28,290
You bet

230
00:15:28,290 --> 00:15:30,500
Even though I have compulsive behavioral disorder

231
00:15:30,500 --> 00:15:32,170
I step up

232
00:15:32,170 --> 00:15:35,080
when it matters.

233
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:37,250
just like you saved my life the other day

234
00:15:51,080 --> 00:15:52,880
Zhen

235
00:15:52,880 --> 00:15:53,790
didn't you say the other day

236
00:15:53,790 --> 00:15:55,920
that you want to sleep through every hotel in Taipei with me?

237
00:15:55,920 --> 00:15:58,790
Why did you invite me home today?

238
00:16:01,630 --> 00:16:04,000
Sorry, I’ve been busy.

239
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:06,170
but I do miss you

240
00:16:06,170 --> 00:16:08,290
I invited you over instead.

241
00:16:08,290 --> 00:16:09,630
You don't like it?

242
00:16:10,710 --> 00:16:12,420
How can I not like it

243
00:16:12,420 --> 00:16:15,040
if I can see you?

244
00:16:17,130 --> 00:16:20,130
Are all companions this cheesy?

245
00:16:20,130 --> 00:16:20,960
Of course not...

246
00:16:20,960 --> 00:16:22,130
If you don't like it

247
00:16:22,130 --> 00:16:24,540
I can switch to my “dorky mode".

248
00:16:24,540 --> 00:16:26,540
Hello, I am Hunter

249
00:16:28,630 --> 00:16:30,170
So dorky, huh...

250
00:16:33,420 --> 00:16:35,130
By the way, is Wang Jianhai

251
00:16:35,130 --> 00:16:36,790
still bothering you?

252
00:16:36,790 --> 00:16:38,790
No... no...

253
00:16:38,790 --> 00:16:41,290
I've had you got my back.

254
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:02,540
Lin Yunru came by.

255
00:17:04,460 --> 00:17:06,960
Didn't she stop going to the club a long time ago?

256
00:17:06,960 --> 00:17:09,750
Why is she going back to support the club now?

257
00:17:13,329 --> 00:17:15,670
She's not here to support

258
00:17:15,670 --> 00:17:17,880
but to complain

259
00:17:17,880 --> 00:17:20,670
She's tricked into signing some IOUs by you

260
00:17:20,670 --> 00:17:23,130
The interest skyrocketed

261
00:17:23,130 --> 00:17:27,000
and ended up being a hostess

262
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:28,790
Isn’t that normal?

263
00:17:28,790 --> 00:17:31,170
That’s how this business works.

264
00:17:31,170 --> 00:17:33,880
She wanted to do it herself, who forced her?

265
00:17:37,580 --> 00:17:39,330
The problem is—

266
00:17:39,330 --> 00:17:41,420
you made her advance the money

267
00:17:41,420 --> 00:17:44,380
and had her signed some IOUs.

268
00:17:44,380 --> 00:17:46,420
Working with loan sharks

269
00:17:46,420 --> 00:17:48,290
is illegal

270
00:17:48,290 --> 00:17:50,040
The police are investigating.

271
00:17:51,540 --> 00:17:53,040
investigating?

272
00:17:54,380 --> 00:17:56,420
What can they do?

273
00:17:56,420 --> 00:17:59,130
No one dares mess with this food chain nowadays

274
00:18:01,790 --> 00:18:04,460
This has blown up.

275
00:18:04,460 --> 00:18:06,420
Lin Yunru isn't the only one

276
00:18:06,420 --> 00:18:09,540
other girls have reported it too.

277
00:18:09,540 --> 00:18:12,000
You should stop now.

278
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:13,420
Don't keep doing that.

279
00:18:15,380 --> 00:18:17,630
Tony…

280
00:18:17,630 --> 00:18:20,250
back when we hung out together

281
00:18:20,250 --> 00:18:22,630
didn't you tell me that

282
00:18:22,630 --> 00:18:25,670
making money fast is what matters.

283
00:18:25,670 --> 00:18:27,540
Look at you now

284
00:18:27,540 --> 00:18:30,500
How long will it take to make enough to live on

285
00:18:30,500 --> 00:18:32,500
relying solely on services and chatting?

286
00:18:33,420 --> 00:18:36,790
In our business, without lending

287
00:18:36,790 --> 00:18:39,250
how do we keep the clients spending more?

288
00:18:39,250 --> 00:18:42,290
Should you consider

289
00:18:42,290 --> 00:18:45,790
bringing the Club into the system?

290
00:18:45,790 --> 00:18:49,250
Give them credit lines,

291
00:18:49,250 --> 00:18:50,670
they can enjoy more fun

292
00:18:50,670 --> 00:18:52,040
and pay it off slowly

